title: John Michael Talbot Discography 1976-2007 (24 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
JOHN MICHAEL TALBOT DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 24 releases...

 * 1976 - John Michael Talbot
 * 1977 - The New Earth
 * 1979 - The Lord's Supper
 * 1980 - Beginnings
 * 1980 - Come To The Quiet
 * 1980 - The Painter
 * 1984 - God Of Life
 * 1985 - The Quiet
 * 1986 - Empty Canvas
 * 1987 - Heart Of The Shepherd
 * 1987 - Quiet Reflections
 * 1990 - Come Worship The Lord - Vol 1
 * 1991 - Come Worship The Lord - Vol 2
 * 1993 - Meditations In The Spirit
 * 1995 - Chant From The Hermitage
 * 1996 - Brother To Brother
 * 1999 - Pathways Of The Shepherd
 * 2000 - Simple Heart
 * 2001 - Wisdom
 * 2003 - Signatures
 * 2005 - City Of God
 * 2005 - Monk Rock
 * 2006 - The Beautiful City
 * 2007 - Living Water

John Michael Talbot is an American Catholic singer-songwriter, guitarist and founder of a monastic community known as the Brothers and Sisters of Charity.
